the new rhapsody - excellent epic symphonic metal no you 're not seeing things . it is rhapsody in all their excess and you know what ? it sounds pretty good . not sure of the reason for the name change but it seems to have made them less hyper and more melodious ( if that 's possible ) . plenty of medieval melodies , soaring vocals , backing choirs and of course , bombast . not unlike luc turilli 's two new separate releases sans the female lead vocalists , but not quite as good . for fans of therion , dreamquest , epica